('2612', '273', '_content_0_subtitle', 'field_59f9de1e78e7f'),
('2613', '273', 'content_0_text', 'Sitindustrie Valvometal started manufacturing valves for the energy industry in 1955 in its plant in Valduggia, Italy, and today is regarded as a very important supplier of ball, gate, globe and check valves.\r\n\r\nThe complete range of valves can be produced in forged and cast carbon steel, stainless steel and special alloy. Our company is mainly focused to critical applications in oil &amp; gas, petrochemical, power generation, nuclear, food and dairy industries.\r\n\r\nThe continuous investments in R&amp;D together with the willing to satisfying our clientsâ needs , allowed Sitindustrie Valvometal to implement new technologies and innovative solutions for the most severe applications.\r\nFurthermore, Sitindustrie Valvometal, thanks to its more than 60 yearsâ experience in the sector and the commitment of the people who are part of it, is a reliable supplier for the most demanding customers.'),
