('4511', '417', 'description', '<h3>Description</h3>\r\nCheck valve is a valve that normally allows fluid to flow through it in only one direction.\r\nCheck valves work automatically and most are not controlled by a person or any external control; accordingly, most do not have any valve handle or stem.\r\nThey are installed both on-shore and off-shore, in the cryogenic and water treatment services, in oil & gas and power generation plants.\r\n\r\n<h3>Design</h3>\r\naccording to API 6D, BS 1868, ASME B16.34, API 602, ISO 15761 â BS 5352\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bolted bonnet and pressure seal design</li>\r\n<li>Swing check and piston check</li>\r\n<li>Internal hinge pin</li>\r\n<li>Full bore api 6d version with optional hydraulic damper</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nFire Safe tested API 6FA, API 607\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Range of production</h3>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-top: 30px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n		<img src=\"http://sitindustrievalvometal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/check-valves_tabella1.png\" width=\"250px;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<strong>BOLTED BONNET</strong>\r\n<table style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ENDS</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">R.F. - R.T.J. - B.W. - S.W. - NPT</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>CLASS</td>\r\n<td>150</td>\r\n<td>300</td>\r\n<td>600</td>\r\n<td>900</td>\r\n<td>1500</td>\r\n<td>2500</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>NPS (up | to)</td>\r\n<td>56\"</td>\r\n<td>48\"</td>\r\n<td>42\"</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>24\"</td>\r\n<td>12\"</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n		<img src=\"http://sitindustrievalvometal.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/check-valves_tabella2.png\" width=\"250px;\">\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n<strong>PRESSURE SEAL</strong>\r\n<table style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ENDS</td>\r\n<td colspan=\"6\">R.F. - R.T.J. - B.W.</td