('4557', '425', 'body_0_text', 'Ital Parts Group successfully reached its 20th year of activity and thanks to all the colleagues, partners and friends that joinined the party, the celebration in Castello Visconti di San Vito was a great and pleasant night spent toghether!\r\n \r\nA lion has been chosen to represent this special event: the symbol of strenght, courage and of passion, which are the main ingredients of this successfull activity.\r\n \r\nWe are very proud about our important worldwide references in many industrial projects, both as a trading company and a manufacturer.\r\n \r\nThanks to the precious help our all that people that helped this starting activity in 1997, which let Ital Parts Group grew its four main fields: Ital Machine, Ital Motors, Italpharchem and Italpetrochem.\r\n \r\nYou are not only a customer or supplier or partner or worker to us, you are part of our growing path, that means that you are part of our capital to keep on this way!\r\n \r\nSee you for the next anniversary!'),
