('5979', '492', 'tabs_0_title', 'Destructive Test'),
('5980', '492', '_tabs_0_title', 'field_5a0880985164f'),
('5981', '492', 'tabs_0_text', 'Raw materials come from qualified suppliers that can guarantee through 3.1 and 3.2 certification:'),
('5982', '492', '_tabs_0_text', 'field_5a0880a251650'),
('5983', '492', 'tabs_0_list', '<ul>\r\n<li>Chemical Analisys</li>\r\n<li>Mechanical Tests</li>\r\n<li>Micrographic examinations</li>\r\n<li>Macrographic examinations</li>\r\n<li>Corrosion tests</li>\r\n<li>Other</li>\r\n</ul>'),
('5984', '492', '_tabs_0_list', 'field_5a0880b451651'),
('5985', '492', 'tabs_1_title', 'Non destructive Test'),
('5986', '492', '_tabs_1_title', 'field_5a0880985164f'),
('5987', '492', 'tabs_1_text', 'Our qualified personnel at level II & III according to ISO 9712/SNT-TC-1A can perform:'),
('5988', '492', '_tabs_1_text', 'field_5a0880a251650'),
('5989', '492', 'tabs_1_list', '<ul>\r\n<li>Visual & Dimensional examinations (VT)</li>\r\n<li>Dye Penetrant Examinations (PT)</li>\r\n<li>Magnetic Particle Examinations (MT)</li>\r\n<li>Ultrasonic Examinations (UT)</li>\r\n<li>Radiographic Examinations (RT)*</li>\r\n<li>Positive Material Examinations (PMI)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<small>*Outsourced</small>'),
('5990', '492', '_tabs_1_list', 'field_5a0880b451651'),
('5991', '492', 'tabs_2_title', 'Valve Test'),
('5992', '492', '_tabs_2_title', 'field_5a0880985164f'),
('5993', '492', 'tabs_2_text', 'Our valves are tested according to the main standards:'),
('5994', '492', '_tabs_2_text', 'field_5a0880a251650'),
('5995', '492', 'tabs_2_list', '<ul>\r\n<li>Hydraulic & Pneumatic test</li>\r\n<li>High pressure gas test</li>\r\n<li>Fugitive emission test</li>\r\n<li>Cryogenic test*</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<small>*Outsourced</small>'),
('5996', '492', '_tabs_2_list', 'field_5a0880b451651'),
('5997', '492', 'tabs_3_title', 'Final Inspections'),
('5998', '492', '_tabs_3_title', 'field_5a0880985164f'),
('5999', '492', 'tabs_3_text', 'We take care of the valve till the end:'),
('6000', '492', '_tabs_3_text', 'field_5a0880a251650'),
